<plot>Mama Bear tells Papa to give their canary a bath. Papa gets the bird angry, Mama calls him a nincompoop, and he goes and sulks in the garage. Young Wilbur comes to cheer him up. He vows to bathe the bird, but in chasing it, lands in the well. Wilbur and Mama raise him and drop him for various reasons.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?422301</url></doc>
